Jan Smithers https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jan_Smithers 0 Karin Jan Smithers (born July 3, 1949) is an American actress. She is best known for playing Bailey Quarters on the CBS sitcom WKRP in Cincinnati (1978–1982). Karin_Jan_Smithers ( born July_3_,_1949 ) is an_American_actress . She is_best_known for playing_Bailey_Quarters on the_CBS_sitcom_WKRP in Cincinnati_(_1978 – 1982_) .
